## Watch out, accumulator 17 works for operations but doesn't print (ever, I think) anything besides 0s.
## Print All of Accumulator 13 digits 
s pr.2 P
s pr.3 P
## Print All of accumulator 20 digits
s pr.15 P
s pr.16 P

